      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">[AZURE.NOTE]</ph> This is not a generic in-browser push notification and is specific to Chrome Apps—see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><ept id=\"p1\">Chrome Apps Overview]</ept> for details.",
